### 🎯 Quick Deploy to Expo Snack

1. **One-Click Deploy**: 
   - Go to [snack.expo.dev](https://snack.expo.dev/)
   - Click "Import from GitHub"
   - Enter: `https://github.com/balamir53/weatherpro`

2. **Manual Deploy**:
   ```bash
   # Clone the repository
   git clone https://github.com/balamir53/weatherpro.git
   cd weatherpro
   
   # Install dependencies
   npm install
   
   # Start with Expo
   expo start
   ```
